view.name: menu_view
view.viewQuerySQL: SELECT STRMCODE, ltrim(sys_connect_by_path (to_char (STRMNAME), ' > '), ' > ') as MENUPATH , STRMNAME AS MENUNAME, STRURL AS MENUURL FROM TB_MENU_DATA MENU WHERE CHARNBSP = '1' AND CHARUSE = '1' AND STRTYPE = 'file' and STRSITE != 'minwon' AND STRURL IS NOT NULL START WITH MENU.STRSITE = 'all' CONNECT BY PRIOR MENU.STRMCODE = MENU.STRMSTEPCODE

view.name: minwonform_view
view.viewQuerySQL: SELECT STRMCODE, ltrim(sys_connect_by_path (to_char (STRMNAME), ' > '), ' > ') as MENUPATH , STRMNAME AS MENUNAME, STRURL AS MENUURL, STRPATH AS FILEPATH, STRTEL AS FILEURL FROM TB_MENU_DATA MENU WHERE CHARNBSP = '1' AND CHARUSE = '1' AND STRTYPE = 'file' and STRSITE = 'minwon' AND STRURL IS NOT NULL START WITH MENU.STRSITE = 'all' CONNECT BY PRIOR MENU.STRMCODE = MENU.STRMSTEPCODE

view.name: product_privs
view.viewQuerySQL: SELECT PRODUCT, USERID, ATTRIBUTE, SCOPE, NUMERIC_VALUE, CHAR_VALUE, DATE_VALUE, LONG_VALUE FROM SQLPLUS_PRODUCT_PROFILE WHERE USERID = 'PUBLIC' OR USER LIKE USERID

view.name: tb_pageadm_data2
view.viewQuerySQL: SELECT STRMNAME AS STRPAGENAME , STRDEPT, STRNAME, STRTEL, CHARETC, REPLACE(REPLACE(STRURL, 'http://water.busan.go.kr',''), 'https://water.busan.go.kr','') AS STRPAGEPATH FROM TB_MENU_DATA WHERE STRTYPE = 'file' AND STRDEPT IS NOT NULL

view.name: webpage_view
view.viewQuerySQL: SELECT STRMCODE, ltrim(sys_connect_by_path (to_char (STRMNAME), ' > '), ' > ') as MENUPATH , STRMNAME AS MENUNAME, STRPATH, STRURL AS MENUURL FROM TB_MENU_DATA MENU WHERE CHARNBSP = '1' AND STRURL IS NOT NULL AND STRPATH IS NOT NULL AND CHARUSE = '1' AND STRTYPE = 'file' AND CHARSEARCH = '1' AND STROPTION = 'page' AND STRPATH IS NOT NULL START WITH MENU.STRSITE = 'all' CONNECT BY PRIOR MENU.STRMCODE = MENU.STRMSTEPCODE
